    ]
  },
  {
    "expectation_id": "意图阶段正确路由",
    "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
    "suspected_locations": [{"stage": "intent_recognition"}],
    "root_cause_hypothesis": "Wrong intent led to stage=non_agent and end_flag=1, prematurely terminating the conversation.",
    "evidence": [
      {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"},
      {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].end_flag", "value": 1}
    ]
  },
  {
    "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
    "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
    "suspected_locations": [{"stage": "intent_recognition"}],
    "root_cause_hypothesis": "The contract expects stage=intent, but intent_recognition produced non_agent due to misclassification.",
    "evidence": [
      {"source": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"},
      {"source": "actual stage", "value": "non_agent"}
    ]
  }
]

这样对于每个未满足的 expectation，我们都给出了归因。

注意，mp_contract:expected_stage 在 attribution_targets 中 assessment 的 evidence_refs 为空，但我们可以用实际证据。没问题。

